  This sketch shows how to write values to Virtual Pins

  NOTE:
  BlynkTimer provides SimpleTimer functionality:
    http://playground.arduino.cc/Code/SimpleTimer

  App project setup:
    Value Display widget attached to Virtual Pin V5
